<L>__{exterior black swamp day}
<A>__{marion rides hard, galloping along a circuitous, barely visible dry trail... a moment later, tarleton and green dragoons follow...}
<L>__{exterior deep in the swamps evening}
<A>__{marion catches up to a dozen of his men, including gabriel and billings. several of the men are badly wounded, barely clinging to their saddles... they ride through the shallow water, get to a fork, split up. as they disappear into the swamp, the sounds of their horses are swallowed up in the loud buzzing of swamp insects and the cries of the swamp birds... a moment later, tarleton and the vanguard of dragoons ride up. tarleton signals stop at the fork... looks... nothing. listens... nothing. chooses a path, the one marion took. rides off, the dragoons following...}
